high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward to the desk.
Pick up the book that is closest to the back of the desk.
Turn around and go to the garbage can, hang a left and go to the bed.
Put the book on the bed between the three computers.
Turn left, go to the desk, turn right, go to the wall, turn left and go to the desk.
Pick up the book that is in front of the coffee cup on the desk.
Turn around and go to the bed, then hang a right, go past the bed and hang a left, go to bed where the computers are at.
Put the book on the bed to the left of the other book.
anns.task_desc: Put two books on a bed.

high_descs: Turn right, walk straight to the desk..
Pick up the book from the desk.
Turn around to face the door, walk straight, turn left to face the bed and walk straight.
Place the book on the bed.
Turn left, walk straight to the desk, turn right when you reach the desk, walk straight to the wall and turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the book on the desk.
Turn around to face the bed, turn right, walk straight to the wall, turn left to face the door, walk straight and turn left to face the bed.
Place the book on the bed next to the other book.
anns.task_desc: Place two books on the bed.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step to the trash can.
Pick up the book to the right of the smartphone on the left side of the desk.
Go over to the bed and face the mattress.
Put the book on the edge of the bed so it's in between the three laptops.
Go back to the desk, but face the right edge of the desk this time.
Pick up the book that's in front of the coffee mug.
Go back to the bed and face the mattress again.
Put the book down in front of the previous book.

Place that book on the bed
Put it in between the computers
